NOTICE / 数据版权说明

The MIT license above covers ONLY the source code in this repository
(helper.py, prepare_data.py, install.sh, SKILL.md authoring, and the JSON
indices generated from the script).

The text of the screenplay 《武林外传》(Wǔlín Wàizhuàn / "My Own Swordsman"),
included in raw form under `武林外传全剧本/` and as derived JSON under
`wulin-dialogue/data/`, is the intellectual property of its original
screenwriter(s) (宁财神 et al.) and producers. It is included in this
repository solely for personal, educational, and research use, and as a
technical demonstration of an LLM skill that performs verbatim retrieval
rather than generative reproduction.

If you are a rights holder and wish the script data to be removed, please
open an issue on this repository and the data will be taken down.

本仓库中的《武林外传》剧本原文（位于 `武林外传全剧本/`）以及由其衍生的
JSON 数据（位于 `wulin-dialogue/data/`），版权归原编剧（宁财神 等）和
制作方所有。仓库收录此数据仅供个人学习、学术研究及技术演示用途。如版权方
有异议，请提交 issue，将立即下线相关数据。
